Happy Earth Day! 🌎 Stellabrate by learning simple ways to be more sustainable around the house! 💡How about repurposing and upscaling all those Stella Rosa bottles? Watch our latest episode of Stellabration Education with Nina Chantele and the Stella Rosa team to get inspired with a few creative DIY bottle crafts! 💚

🌟 Don’t forget to enter the Green Queen Giveaway by submitting a pic of your creation for your chance to win a $500 Visa gift card and merch! 

Visit the 🔗 in our bio to enter!

node.title: Stellabration Education Episode 3: DIY Bottle Crafts

Embrace your enchant-mint for sparkly Stella Rosa cocktails and fix yourself this mouth-watering cocktail ft. @DoleSunshine Pineapple juice! 😋✨⁣
⁣
💞 Enchant-Mint Mojito ⁣
⁣
- Stella Rosa® Prosecco⁣
- 4 oz Dole® Pineapple juice⁣
- Gold Stella Rosa® Sparkles⁣
- 1 oz rum⁣
- Mango and lime slices⁣
- Mint⁣
⁣
𝐃𝐢𝐫𝐞𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐬:⁣
1. In a shaker, muddle together mint, mango slices, a squeeze of lime juice, and rum.⁣
2. Add pineapple juice and top off with Stella Rosa® Prosecco. If desired, add a pinch of Gold Stella Rosa® Sparkles!⁣
3. Stir and strain over ice into a short cocktail glass. Garnish with mint, mango, and lime slices. Enjoy!⁣

Have a sparkling Fourth of July! 💖🇺🇸 Stellabrate® with a cocktail that'll outshine all the fireworks in the sky. 🎆See below for recipe 👇⁣
⁣
🎇Firework Fiesta ⁣
- Stella Rosa Platinum French Vanilla
- Mixed red berries
- Blue curaçao 
- Honey (for rim)
- Red edible drink glitter (for rim)
⁣
𝐈𝐧𝐬𝐭𝐫𝐮𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐬:⁣
1. Rim the glasses with honey and roll in red edible drink glitter⁣.
2. In the glass, muddle berries and top with crushed ice. 
3. Top with Stella Rosa Platinum French Vanilla. 
4. With an upside down cocktail spoon, pour a small amount of blue curaçao to create a red, white, and blue effect! Enjoy!
⁣
⁣
